Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.62,0:19:07.63,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\fnMYoyo HK Medium\blur2}釘下終焉之樁
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.63,0:19:12.42,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\fnMYoyo HK Medium\blur2}歪著頭的人偶笑聲空洞
