Comment: 1,0:19:21.72,0:19:23.35,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\fnMYoyo HK Medium\blur2}La La La La La La Lan
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.35,0:19:26.58,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\fnMYoyo HK Medium\blur2}撕碎成無數片變為繁星
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.58,0:19:28.31,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\fnMYoyo HK Medium\blur2}侵蝕你的內心
